anyhow = "1.0.69"

[workspace.dependencies.gstreamer]
version = "0.20.2"
features = ["v1_18"]

bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/bin/server.rs"
name = "server"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"

[dependencies.clap]

[dependencies.config]
workspace = true

[dependencies.gst-plugin-fallbackswitch]

[dependencies.gstreamer]

[dependencies.gstreamer-sdp]

[dependencies.serde]
workspace = true

[dependencies.shared]
path = "../shared"

[dependencies.tokio]

features = ["full"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "server"

doc = true

harness = true
edition = "2021"
